                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-2-defend54 t18000115-2-punish11"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 34.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
